    metaDescription: "Sweep your partner off their feet without emptying your bank account. These romantic resort deals deliver candlelit dinners, spa treatments, and serious couple time.",
    category: "interests",
    publishDate: "2026-03-03",
    author: "VacationDeals.to Staff",
    readTime: "9 min read",
    bluf: "Romance doesn't require a royal budget. These 7 resort deals deliver genuine couple experiences — spa packages, sunset dinners, and adults-only pools — at prices that won't cause a fight about finances on the way home.",
