    title: "7 Best Theme Park Vacation Deals Near Disney and Universal",
    metaTitle: "7 Best Theme Park Vacation Deals (2026)",
    metaDescription: "Theme park vacation deals near Disney World, Universal Studios, and more. Stay at resort properties minutes from the action and save big on your theme park trip.",
